data.description: This stylish three bedroom Contemporary Cape is set on over an acre of property conveniently located near shopping and the Taconic Parkway. Features include a landscaped walkway, pressure treated front deck, Anderson windows, rear stone patio, oversized two car garage, bamboo and hardwood flooring, and additional level yard area perfect for pool or playset. Inside you'll find the Living Room with dramatic vaulted ceiling, a formal Dining Room, spacious eat-in Kitchen, a generous Master Bedroom and a full bath with dual entry on the first level. Upstairs there are two additional bedrooms, a den/office and a loft space overlooking the Living Room plus a full bath. Wonderful space for working from home while enjoying the countryside and peaceful surroundings. There is also a full basement for all your storage needs. Just waiting for your personal touch...come take a look while it lasts.
